WEBVTT

00:11.110 --> 00:17.150
[The Coffin of He Jingyuan,
General of Loyalty of Great Yin]

00:17.210 --> 00:19.980
[In Memoriam]

00:20.070 --> 00:21.790
[In memory of He Jingyuan, Governor of Jizhou]

00:28.960 --> 00:30.760
Rest in peace, General He!

00:36.240 --> 00:38.030
Rest in peace, General He!

00:54.490 --> 00:55.920
[In memory of He Jingyuan, Governor of Jizhou]

00:55.950 --> 00:57.880
[In Memory of My Late Father, Xie Linshan]

00:56.150 --> 00:56.980
General He...

00:59.280 --> 01:00.290
rest in peace.

01:10.930 --> 01:15.560
[Wei Qilin, Traitor of Great Yin]

01:16.480 --> 01:17.640
Wei Qilin,

01:18.350 --> 01:20.310
you despicable traitor!

01:21.560 --> 01:23.200
That bastard Wei fled
to escape his crimes back then.

01:23.200 --> 01:24.440
He deserved to fall off that cliff

01:23.940 --> 01:26.190
[Wei Qilin, Traitor of Great Yin]

01:24.510 --> 01:25.310
and have his whole family die.

01:25.310 --> 01:25.910
Served him right!

01:25.910 --> 01:26.470
Served him right!

01:26.470 --> 01:26.950
Served him right!

01:26.950 --> 01:28.840
General He also died in battle yesterday.

01:28.840 --> 01:29.870
Let's beat this bastard Wei together!

01:29.870 --> 01:30.920
-Beat the bastard Wei!
-Beat the bastard Wei!

01:30.920 --> 01:33.450
-Beat the bastard Wei!
-Beat the bastard Wei!

01:34.000 --> 01:34.710
Burn him!

01:34.870 --> 01:37.470
Send him down to apologize to the two generals!

01:39.970 --> 01:41.509
[Wei Qilin, Traitor of Great Yin]

01:42.560 --> 01:43.620
What are you doing?

01:46.920 --> 01:48.150
You are that...

01:48.590 --> 01:51.320
female general who killed Lord Changxin, right?

01:51.590 --> 01:52.880
Yes, it's her.

01:53.000 --> 01:53.950
-It's Mrs. Fan.
-It's her.

01:53.950 --> 01:54.870
It's Mrs. Fan!

01:55.560 --> 01:57.509
Mrs. Fan, what are you doing?

01:57.710 --> 01:59.509
We want to burn this bastard Wei.

02:01.040 --> 02:02.100
He is not a bastard.

02:02.510 --> 02:03.310
Mrs. Fan!

02:04.510 --> 02:06.230
We admire that you, as a woman,

02:06.680 --> 02:08.710
fearlessly killed Lord Changxin.

02:08.710 --> 02:10.360
But why are you speaking up for Wei Qilin,

02:10.360 --> 02:11.560
that traitor?

02:11.560 --> 02:12.910
-I...
-What do you mean?

02:12.910 --> 02:14.710
Why are you defending Wei Qilin?

02:15.030 --> 02:16.960
He's... He's not a traitor.

02:16.960 --> 02:20.000
Today is the death anniversary
of General Xie and General He.

02:20.000 --> 02:20.800
By doing this,

02:20.850 --> 02:22.430
you're making enemies

02:22.450 --> 02:23.730
of the entire Jizhou Army and Yanzhou Army!

02:23.730 --> 02:25.270
I am sorry, Generals.

02:25.560 --> 02:28.820
-But he's really not like that...
-Stop talking nonsense!

02:28.840 --> 02:29.430
Enough!

02:34.800 --> 02:36.030
-My Lord.
-My Lord.

02:46.120 --> 02:46.710
Let's go.

02:56.470 --> 02:58.800
I haven't paid respect to General Xie yet.

02:58.910 --> 03:00.440
I really want to do that.

03:01.430 --> 03:03.120
If you speak up for the bastard Wei,

03:03.120 --> 03:05.120
you are not worthy
to pay respects to General Xie!

03:05.120 --> 03:07.090
The Xie Army will never agree to it!

03:07.240 --> 03:07.670
Yes!

03:07.690 --> 03:08.030
Right!

03:08.030 --> 03:08.690
We will never agree!

03:08.690 --> 03:09.920
-Get out!
-Get out!

03:09.950 --> 03:11.150
-Fall in!
-Get out!

03:35.120 --> 03:36.470
My Lord, what are you...

03:36.470 --> 03:37.829
My Lord, she just...

03:37.860 --> 03:40.390
Xie Army, Yanzhou Army,
listen to my command!

03:43.450 --> 03:44.010
Kneel!

03:58.030 --> 03:58.990
Generals,

04:00.960 --> 04:02.040
rest in peace.

04:01.890 --> 04:03.650
[In memory of He Jingyuan, Governor of Jizhou]

04:03.670 --> 04:05.310
[In Memory of My Late Father, Xie Linshan]

05:41.980 --> 05:46.480
[Pursuit of Jade]

05:46.600 --> 05:49.120
[Episode 31]

06:06.160 --> 06:06.920
Changyu.

06:08.830 --> 06:10.160
Are you feeling better?

06:24.040 --> 06:25.310
I, Fan Changyu,

06:26.430 --> 06:28.290
pay my respects to Your Lordship.

06:31.240 --> 06:32.310
What did you just

06:33.800 --> 06:34.720
call me?

06:36.630 --> 06:37.490
Your Lordship.

06:39.240 --> 06:40.570
You thought for so long,

06:41.480 --> 06:43.210
and that is all you came up with?

06:48.000 --> 06:49.310
Your Lordship?

06:52.040 --> 06:53.920
We really are distant.

06:55.270 --> 06:57.510
Your Lordship, if you feel we're distant,

06:57.510 --> 06:59.710
since we studied under the same master,

07:00.040 --> 07:01.700
you may simply call me Junior.

07:08.070 --> 07:09.970
Your Lordship, this is a restricted area,

07:09.970 --> 07:11.100
and it is my boudoir.

07:11.510 --> 07:13.770
Please behave yourself, Your Lordship.

07:15.630 --> 07:16.680
I might know

07:18.730 --> 07:20.040
what is bothering you.

07:20.680 --> 07:22.010
But you should also know

07:22.310 --> 07:23.680
that nothing in this world

07:23.680 --> 07:24.980
can make us distant.

07:26.160 --> 07:27.960
What if this matter is so serious

07:28.240 --> 07:29.900
that you might not be able to be

07:30.480 --> 07:32.880
the commander of the Yanzhou Army anymore?

07:41.480 --> 07:43.390
Whether I am fit to be a commander

07:43.920 --> 07:45.750
depends entirely on my own ability.

07:45.750 --> 07:48.480
It has nothing to do with anyone or anything else.

07:48.790 --> 07:49.650
Including you.

07:51.240 --> 07:52.900
Your Lordship, are you saying

07:53.120 --> 07:54.850
that everything in this world,

07:56.430 --> 07:58.159
like military affairs,

08:01.270 --> 08:02.950
is decided by you alone?

08:20.390 --> 08:21.450
It's getting late.

08:22.270 --> 08:24.160
I need to recover from my injuries.

08:24.160 --> 08:25.820
Please leave, Your Lordship.

08:54.860 --> 08:57.150
[Jinghe Gate]

08:56.670 --> 08:57.800
Prime Minister Wei!

08:58.630 --> 08:59.760
Prime Minister Wei!

09:02.390 --> 09:03.270
Grand Tutor.

09:04.320 --> 09:05.670
See?

09:05.750 --> 09:06.840
When a man gets old,

09:07.240 --> 09:08.790
his students become more headstrong

09:08.790 --> 09:10.590
and can no longer be controlled.

09:12.910 --> 09:16.000
This proposal concerns the military power of the Jizhou Army.

09:16.000 --> 09:18.910
It is based on merit, with absolutely no bias.

09:19.670 --> 09:22.910
I hope you won't take it to heart, Prime Minister Wei.

09:24.390 --> 09:26.850
If you feel you are getting old, Grand Tutor,

09:27.390 --> 09:29.750
you might learn from Grand Tutor Tao back then

09:29.750 --> 09:31.960
and retire while it's still not too late.

09:31.960 --> 09:34.020
To this day, the court and the public,

09:34.120 --> 09:35.320
and even His Majesty,

09:35.870 --> 09:37.530
remember only his good deeds.

09:37.750 --> 09:40.510
It is better than refusing to retire at seventy,

09:41.440 --> 09:42.840
flaunting your seniority,

09:42.840 --> 09:44.840
and being unable to manage affairs.

09:49.630 --> 09:51.120
He's still so arrogant?

09:52.120 --> 09:54.380
General He fell in the Battle of Lucheng.

09:54.790 --> 09:56.870
In his final memorial,

09:56.910 --> 09:59.670
General He strongly recommended Li Huai'an as Discipline Inspector.

09:59.670 --> 10:02.870
Now that the military power of Jizhou has fallen into other hands,

10:02.870 --> 10:05.870
I'm afraid Wei Yan won't be arrogant for much longer.

10:06.600 --> 10:10.000
As long as the Marquis of Wu'an is still stationed in Lucheng,

10:11.200 --> 10:14.150
the military power won't fall to anyone else.

10:14.630 --> 10:15.320
This is

10:16.230 --> 10:18.630
where Wei Yan's confidence comes from.

10:19.060 --> 10:22.790
[Qinwen Hall]

10:33.840 --> 10:34.720
Mother,

10:34.720 --> 10:38.630
I won't play
the "Big Traitor" game anymore.

10:41.140 --> 10:42.530
You are just children.

10:43.270 --> 10:44.200
What do you know?

10:45.320 --> 10:46.480
How many in this world

10:46.480 --> 10:47.740
can truly distinguish

10:48.200 --> 10:49.720
loyalty from treachery

10:50.600 --> 10:51.800
and right from wrong?

11:00.320 --> 11:01.120
Time to eat.

11:04.480 --> 11:06.240
Alright! Let's go eat.

11:23.480 --> 11:25.550
Father, Mother.

11:26.670 --> 11:28.720
What happened exactly?

11:33.600 --> 11:34.150
Come in.

11:35.630 --> 11:36.320
Fan.

11:36.630 --> 11:37.240
Boss.

11:38.870 --> 11:39.600
-Fan.
-Boss.

11:41.320 --> 11:42.400
Generals,

11:42.550 --> 11:43.360
what are you here for?

11:43.360 --> 11:44.320
It's been days.

11:44.320 --> 11:46.000
General Fan, can you drink now?

11:46.000 --> 11:48.240
-Exactly.
-We've been waiting for so many days.

11:48.240 --> 11:50.360
We've wanted to celebrate for a while.

11:50.360 --> 11:51.100
Right?

11:51.270 --> 11:52.270
What General Fan?

11:52.600 --> 11:53.550
You flatter me.

11:53.960 --> 11:56.120
General Fan, you are a great general in our eyes.

11:56.120 --> 11:58.120
You are the hero who killed Lord Changxin.

11:58.120 --> 11:59.630
Recovering Chongzhou is just around the corner.

11:59.630 --> 12:00.120
After that,

12:00.120 --> 12:01.790
there won't be any battles left to fight.

12:01.790 --> 12:02.600
-Right.
-Yeah.

12:02.600 --> 12:03.150
Let's drink.

12:03.150 --> 12:03.910
Come on, Boss.

12:03.910 --> 12:05.910
-Fan, let me fill your cup.
-Come on.

12:07.030 --> 12:07.720
Here, Fan.

12:09.240 --> 12:10.840
Thank you, guys.

12:10.840 --> 12:11.300
Cheers!

12:11.670 --> 12:12.930
-Bottoms up.
-Cheers.

12:14.080 --> 12:14.840
Sister!

12:18.550 --> 12:19.750
-Have some?
-Sister.

12:19.790 --> 12:21.590
Well... Lord Li wants to see you.

12:22.750 --> 12:23.750
Let him in then.

12:24.630 --> 12:26.560
That might... not be appropriate.

12:26.670 --> 12:29.070
Sister, you'd better go out and take a look.

12:29.420 --> 12:37.720
[Qinwen Hall]

12:36.440 --> 12:38.720
Lord Li, what are you doing?

12:39.600 --> 12:40.600
I am ashamed.

12:41.360 --> 12:44.290
Today I came with thorned sticks
to apologize to you.

12:44.600 --> 12:45.660
My first sin is that

12:47.080 --> 12:49.010
when the rebels attacked the city,

12:49.200 --> 12:51.030
you were afraid I would act impulsively,

12:51.030 --> 12:52.230
so you knocked me out.

12:52.600 --> 12:54.790
I did not understand your good intentions,

12:54.790 --> 12:58.190
and instead spoke harshly to you when you were seriously ill.

12:58.440 --> 12:59.640
This was unjust of me.

13:00.750 --> 13:01.880
My second sin is that

13:02.510 --> 13:03.480
my dispute with you

13:03.480 --> 13:05.480
caused others to misunderstand you

13:05.720 --> 13:07.380
and damaged your reputation.

13:07.750 --> 13:09.410
This was disrespectful of me.

13:10.360 --> 13:11.480
Mrs. Fan,

13:12.360 --> 13:14.690
please whip me with these thorned sticks.

13:15.790 --> 13:17.790
Otherwise, I have no face to see you,

13:18.630 --> 13:20.510
nor to see Lord He.

13:36.840 --> 13:38.100
Lord Li, don't mind it.

13:38.600 --> 13:40.200
Lord He treated me very well.

13:40.240 --> 13:42.630
I can understand your situation at that time.

13:42.630 --> 13:43.120
Please get up.

13:43.120 --> 13:44.000
I am ashamed.

13:45.030 --> 13:48.550
I didn't expect that, with so many years
of experience in the Northwest,

13:48.550 --> 13:50.840
my judgment
would still fall short of yours.

13:50.840 --> 13:53.040
You just lost composure out of concern.

13:53.600 --> 13:55.200
Don't be so hard on yourself.

13:57.390 --> 13:58.550
I knocked you out,

13:58.790 --> 13:59.790
so I was wrong too.

14:00.550 --> 14:02.240
One wrong cancels out the other.

14:02.240 --> 14:03.300
Let's call it even.

14:04.600 --> 14:05.180
Get up.

14:12.270 --> 14:13.790
Eenie meenie miney moe,

14:13.540 --> 14:19.610
[East Suburb of Qingping County]

14:13.790 --> 14:15.240
catch a tiger by the toe.

14:15.390 --> 14:16.450
I'll take this one.

14:16.910 --> 14:18.240
No peeking.

14:18.790 --> 14:20.440
I want the highest one.

14:20.840 --> 14:22.360
Look at my Double Heaven card.

14:22.360 --> 14:24.440
Look at my "Four Pairs of Candied Haws."

14:24.440 --> 14:26.200
Look, did I win?

14:26.550 --> 14:27.480
I won.

14:27.720 --> 14:28.630
I won.

14:28.790 --> 14:30.200
It was me who won.

14:30.200 --> 14:31.960
-Who won?
-Mr. Zhao, look.

14:31.960 --> 14:33.200
Who won?

14:33.200 --> 14:34.360
Double Heaven crushes them all,

14:34.360 --> 14:35.510
like an emperor ruling everything.

14:35.510 --> 14:36.770
Bao'er won this round.

14:38.840 --> 14:39.870
Come on. One more round.

14:39.870 --> 14:41.960
One more round. One more.

14:41.960 --> 14:44.390
-Okay. Enough.
-I'll take the Thunder card and blow you up.

14:44.390 --> 14:46.120
I want the Empress card.

15:01.120 --> 15:01.930
Come on.

15:02.480 --> 15:03.120
Don't run.

15:04.630 --> 15:05.560
They're with us.

15:17.010 --> 15:25.620
[Grass Cottage]

15:27.840 --> 15:28.550
Bao'er.

15:29.960 --> 15:30.880
Changning.

15:35.510 --> 15:36.750
Fairy Sister!

15:43.080 --> 15:45.320
Mother, you're finally back.

15:45.750 --> 15:46.910
I missed you so much.

15:48.960 --> 15:50.400
I missed you too.

15:53.200 --> 15:54.120
Manager Yu.

15:55.030 --> 15:56.200
You're back?

16:05.240 --> 16:06.390
It was Changyu

16:06.390 --> 16:08.250
who had General Qi escort me back.

16:08.840 --> 16:11.980
She said not a single person from Lin'an
can be left behind.

16:11.980 --> 16:12.710
I...

16:14.200 --> 16:15.330
am from Lin'an, too.

16:15.870 --> 16:17.960
Changyu is so capable.

16:18.320 --> 16:20.390
She sent Changning, Bao'er, and me

16:20.390 --> 16:21.390
back here before.

16:21.910 --> 16:23.660
And now she's brought back another one.

16:23.660 --> 16:25.240
I'm glad you're back.

16:25.550 --> 16:27.720
One missing piece of this family
is finally back.

16:27.720 --> 16:28.480
Yes.

16:33.580 --> 16:36.250
[Jizhou Government Office]

17:08.480 --> 17:09.740
Why are you still here?

17:10.160 --> 17:10.829
What?

17:11.750 --> 17:12.310
Let's go!

17:29.720 --> 17:30.440
Tell me now!

17:30.510 --> 17:33.160
Sir, the Marquis of Wu'an said
he was busy with military affairs

17:33.160 --> 17:33.920
and couldn't come.

17:33.920 --> 17:35.180
He told you not to wait.

17:38.720 --> 17:40.790
Sir, if we don't read
the imperial edict now,

17:40.790 --> 17:42.720
we might miss the auspicious hour.

17:48.070 --> 17:48.680
Fine.

17:49.350 --> 17:50.880
Let's not wait for him then.

17:51.170 --> 17:52.080
Well,

17:54.250 --> 17:56.230
read the first two decrees first.

17:56.260 --> 18:02.580
[Qinwen Hall]

17:59.030 --> 18:00.070
Why did you drag me here?

18:00.070 --> 18:00.960
I was stewing meat.

18:00.960 --> 18:01.720
Hurry up.

18:12.270 --> 18:13.110
What took you so long?

18:13.110 --> 18:14.160
Why are there so many people?

18:14.160 --> 18:14.890
You're here?

18:24.690 --> 18:26.820
How long will reading the edicts take?

18:27.590 --> 18:29.070
In the shadow puppet plays,

18:29.070 --> 18:30.590
it only takes a little while.

18:30.590 --> 18:32.590
I don't know why this is taking so long.

18:32.590 --> 18:33.680
Yeah. Even at my grandfather's wake,

18:33.680 --> 18:34.350
I didn't kneel this long.

18:34.350 --> 18:36.000
I can't feel my knees now.

18:36.030 --> 18:36.890
Get lost!

18:39.590 --> 18:40.930
My stewed meat...

18:41.290 --> 18:48.030
[Qinwu Hall]

18:51.200 --> 18:55.070
Here come the Imperial Decrees!

18:53.620 --> 18:55.730
[Qinwen Hall]

18:57.310 --> 19:00.310
Soldiers, receive the decrees!

19:01.960 --> 19:04.200
His Majesty decrees:

19:04.590 --> 19:06.200
The rebels of Chongzhou

19:06.270 --> 19:08.070
disrupted the realm of Great Yin

19:08.200 --> 19:09.750
and oppressed the people.

19:10.030 --> 19:13.750
He Jingyuan, Governor of Jizhou,
valiantly upheld the state,

19:13.790 --> 19:15.400
vanquished the rebels,

19:15.480 --> 19:19.080
and perished heroically on the battlefield for his country.

19:19.270 --> 19:21.030
Moved by his loyalty and merit,

19:21.110 --> 19:23.000
His Majesty posthumously confers upon him

19:23.000 --> 19:26.880
the title of General of Rectitude.

19:27.070 --> 19:30.310
He shall be buried with state honors

19:30.590 --> 19:34.070
to honor his loyalty and courage
and console his heroic spirit.

19:34.070 --> 19:37.200
Let this proclamation be known
throughout the land.

19:37.550 --> 19:41.540
[Qinwu Hall]

19:37.920 --> 19:41.880
Li Huai'an, Martial Commandant of Jizhou,

19:42.960 --> 19:44.240
remained calm in danger

19:44.240 --> 19:46.110
and displayed great merit
in defending the city.

19:46.110 --> 19:48.240
He is hereby appointed
Discipline Inspector of Jizhou

19:48.240 --> 19:51.400
and rewarded, along with his subordinates,

19:51.400 --> 19:54.860
with 200 taels of gold
and 800 taels of silver.

19:54.960 --> 19:57.160
Thank you for your grace, Your Majesty.

20:05.750 --> 20:08.920
Soldier of Jizhou, Fan Changyu.

20:12.790 --> 20:14.160
Fan Changyu!

20:15.200 --> 20:16.550
Where did Fan go?

20:16.590 --> 20:17.750
Fan Changyu!

20:18.200 --> 20:19.160
I don't know.

20:19.160 --> 20:20.270
Fan Changyu!

20:25.310 --> 20:27.000
Soldier of Jizhou,

20:28.310 --> 20:29.790
Fan Changyu,

20:30.350 --> 20:32.790
killed Lord Changxin on the battlefield

20:32.790 --> 20:34.350
and achieved remarkable merit.

20:34.350 --> 20:36.830
She is hereby appointed Chief Commandant,

20:36.920 --> 20:39.110
ranking junior fifth rank,

20:39.220 --> 20:42.070
-and rewarded, along with her subordinates,
-Fifth rank?

20:42.070 --> 20:45.440
-with 100 taels of gold and 500 taels of silver.
-Fifth rank!

20:45.680 --> 20:46.510
Fifth rank!

20:46.420 --> 20:50.330
[Qinwu Hall]

20:46.510 --> 20:50.720
Considering that the Jizhou Army cannot
go a single day without leadership,

20:50.720 --> 20:54.590
Li Huaian, the Discipline Inspector,
is appointed as the chief,

20:54.640 --> 20:58.470
with Fan Changyu, the Chief Commandant,
as his deputy,

20:58.550 --> 21:01.830
to jointly command the forces of Jizhou

21:01.960 --> 21:03.820
to stabilize the troops' morale.

21:04.030 --> 21:06.070
Let this proclamation be made known,

21:06.070 --> 21:07.960
that all concerned may take heed.

21:15.480 --> 21:19.140
Discipline Inspector Li, please accept
the decree on her behalf.

21:19.680 --> 21:21.940
Thank you, Your Majesty, for your grace.

21:23.830 --> 21:26.360
Congratulations, Discipline Inspector Li.

21:26.920 --> 21:27.960
Sir, you have traveled far.

21:27.960 --> 21:29.160
The journey must have been exhausting.

21:29.160 --> 21:30.160
If you don't mind,

21:30.270 --> 21:31.730
please take a rest for now.

21:31.960 --> 21:32.420
Please.

21:32.720 --> 21:33.200
Please.

21:34.380 --> 21:40.480
[Qinwen Hall]

21:39.160 --> 21:40.350
-Congratulations!
-Congratulations!

21:40.350 --> 21:41.440
Boss is an official now.

21:41.440 --> 21:42.590
-Great!
-Fan is an official now!

21:42.590 --> 21:43.850
Fan is an official now!

21:44.750 --> 21:45.480
Chief Commandant!

21:45.480 --> 21:45.920
Five hundred taels!

21:45.920 --> 21:47.960
I have served in the palace for many years

21:47.960 --> 21:51.000
but have never seen such
unruly ruffian soldiers.

21:51.440 --> 21:52.350
How did they

21:52.490 --> 21:55.080
manage to defeat Lord Changxin?

21:58.640 --> 21:59.310
Commandant Fan is over there!

21:59.310 --> 22:00.160
-Come on.
-Let's go.

22:00.160 --> 22:01.360
-Let's go.
-Let's go.

22:02.240 --> 22:03.170
Commandant Fan.

22:03.920 --> 22:04.850
Commandant Fan.

22:10.510 --> 22:11.180
Commandant Fan,

22:11.180 --> 22:12.920
we failed to recognize your greatness before.

22:12.920 --> 22:13.790
Please forgive our offense.

22:13.790 --> 22:14.760
-Sorry.
-Sorry.

22:14.790 --> 22:16.070
What did you call me?

22:16.200 --> 22:17.030
Commandant Fan.

22:17.030 --> 22:17.680
Fan!

22:18.510 --> 22:19.240
Where is Fan?

22:21.000 --> 22:21.790
Congratulations, Fan!

22:21.790 --> 22:22.920
-Congratulations!
-Congratulations, Sister!

22:22.920 --> 22:23.550
You're an official now!

22:23.550 --> 22:24.550
An official?

22:25.030 --> 22:25.720
What official?

22:25.720 --> 22:26.790
Chief Commandant.

22:26.790 --> 22:28.250
Appointed by His Majesty.

22:28.330 --> 22:29.070
Fifth rank.

22:29.070 --> 22:29.680
Fifth rank.

22:29.680 --> 22:30.550
They say since the founding of the dynasty,

22:30.550 --> 22:31.550
there has never been a woman

22:31.550 --> 22:32.790
who held such a high official position.

22:32.790 --> 22:33.850
And another thing.

22:33.960 --> 22:35.110
From now on, when the Magistrate sees you,

22:35.110 --> 22:36.720
he has to kowtow three times first

22:36.720 --> 22:37.720
before he is allowed to speak to you.

22:37.720 --> 22:39.000
How prestigious!

22:39.350 --> 22:40.000
Really?

22:40.440 --> 22:42.030
Sister, you really are a female general now.

22:42.030 --> 22:43.090
Following the Boss,

22:43.090 --> 22:44.960
we'll live in luxury from now on!

22:44.960 --> 22:45.350
Live in luxury?

22:45.350 --> 22:46.750
We'll have whatever we want!

22:46.750 --> 22:47.670
But remember,

22:47.790 --> 22:49.400
we're riding on Fan's coattails.

22:49.400 --> 22:51.440
Fan, I won't be called Jin Yuanbao anymore.

22:51.440 --> 22:52.680
I'll be called Jin Changsheng.

22:52.680 --> 22:54.640
The three of them are changing their names too.

22:54.640 --> 22:55.310
Manshi.

22:55.350 --> 22:55.720
Right.

22:55.720 --> 22:57.200
Manjun, Mandan.

22:57.480 --> 22:58.400
That's great.

22:58.550 --> 23:01.010
I'm treating everyone to stewed meat today!

23:01.790 --> 23:02.400
Come on.

23:03.350 --> 23:04.030
Come on.

23:04.240 --> 23:05.030
Let's help out.

23:05.030 --> 23:06.000
-Come on!
-Come on!

23:06.000 --> 23:06.720
Sit down.

23:06.750 --> 23:07.750
Go sit over there.

23:07.750 --> 23:08.880
-Okay.
-Okay.

23:09.310 --> 23:10.830
Sister, let me get the bowls.

23:10.830 --> 23:11.550
Boss, sit!

23:11.880 --> 23:13.410
Here, let me fill your cups!

23:13.790 --> 23:14.440
Here.

23:16.920 --> 23:17.510
Take this over there.

23:17.510 --> 23:18.030
Okay.

23:19.720 --> 23:20.110
Here.

23:20.550 --> 23:21.240
Thank you.

23:21.270 --> 23:22.180
Okay.

23:22.720 --> 23:23.180
Come on.

23:23.240 --> 23:23.880
Come on.

23:24.160 --> 23:24.640
No need for too much.

23:24.640 --> 23:25.640
Two big bowls will be enough.

23:25.640 --> 23:26.700
Take it over there.

23:26.880 --> 23:27.210
Here.

23:28.000 --> 23:28.980
Here, Generals.

23:30.110 --> 23:31.080
Enjoy.

23:31.140 --> 23:32.200
Such a big portion.

23:32.400 --> 23:33.240
Enjoy!

23:33.440 --> 23:34.100
Bottoms up!

23:34.350 --> 23:35.480
Let me fill your cup.

23:35.920 --> 23:36.590
Drink up!

23:48.800 --> 23:52.200
Discipline Inspector Li, you must be
very disappointed, aren't you?

23:52.200 --> 23:54.400
You thought that now General He is gone,

23:54.790 --> 23:55.900
the military power

23:56.270 --> 23:58.680
would naturally fall to your Li family.

23:58.960 --> 24:01.620
But unexpectedly,
half of it was snatched away.

24:03.350 --> 24:05.480
Such a trifle wouldn't disappoint me.

24:06.510 --> 24:07.840
But you, Your Lordship.

24:07.920 --> 24:10.000
The military power of Jizhou
is so important.

24:10.000 --> 24:12.160
Why was it handed
to a young lady with neither experience

24:12.160 --> 24:13.880
nor background?

24:21.800 --> 24:25.570
Didn't you report her merits to the Imperial Court
on your own accord?

24:25.570 --> 24:26.770
This is the result.

24:29.680 --> 24:31.280
I reported Mrs. Fan's merits

24:31.400 --> 24:32.400
to protect her.

24:33.170 --> 24:35.300
And I will certainly protect her well.

24:38.790 --> 24:39.920
My wife

24:40.440 --> 24:42.480
does not need an outsider like you
to protect her.

24:42.480 --> 24:43.270
Wife?

24:44.690 --> 24:47.550
I remember Mrs. Fan married Yan Zheng
back then,

24:47.590 --> 24:48.650
not you, Xie Zheng.

24:49.000 --> 24:50.200
Even if it were Yan Zheng,

24:50.200 --> 24:52.070
you two have signed the Divorce Agreement.

24:52.070 --> 24:54.310
Today, Mrs. Fan
has no marital relationship with you.

24:54.310 --> 24:56.880
Your Lordship, why deceive yourself?

25:02.200 --> 25:04.460
Discipline Inspector Li, don't forget.

25:04.680 --> 25:07.410
Your betrothal to the Princess Royal
is settled.

25:07.720 --> 25:09.150
Two-timing

25:09.350 --> 25:11.210
is not the conduct of a gentleman.

25:29.480 --> 25:31.510
Xie Qi has escorted Yu Qianqian safely.

25:31.510 --> 25:32.570
But Grand Tutor Tao

25:32.790 --> 25:33.920
insists on staying.

25:34.510 --> 25:36.000
He just refuses to return to the capital

25:36.000 --> 25:37.060
to resume his post.

25:37.310 --> 25:38.510
If he doesn't go back,

25:39.240 --> 25:41.400
I'm afraid His Majesty will be displeased.

25:41.400 --> 25:42.660
What are you afraid of?

25:43.750 --> 25:46.310
His Majesty has always been
a fence-sitter,

25:46.680 --> 25:49.010
looking for someone powerful to cling to.

25:50.960 --> 25:51.720
Also,

25:52.720 --> 25:55.720
the Imperial Court
handing military power to Mrs. Fan

25:56.310 --> 26:00.240
is likely the result of the struggle
between Wei Yan and Grand Tutor Li.

26:00.310 --> 26:01.400
These two

26:02.350 --> 26:04.150
are keeping each other in check,

26:04.680 --> 26:06.340
so they both decided to let go.

26:06.350 --> 26:08.590
Fan Changyu poses no threat to them.

26:09.400 --> 26:12.000
It's better than me
taking the military power.

26:13.270 --> 26:15.400
Li Huai'an thought he was being clever

26:16.310 --> 26:18.370
but ended up being used by both sides.

26:18.920 --> 26:20.420
These two old foxes.

26:21.310 --> 26:23.270
Their scheming is so blatant

26:23.510 --> 26:25.910
that we can sense it clearly
even in Jizhou.

26:27.480 --> 26:28.720
In this case,

26:29.160 --> 26:31.160
Mrs. Fan is like a child holding gold

26:31.160 --> 26:32.560
walking in a busy market.

26:35.110 --> 26:36.310
She is in big trouble.

26:37.590 --> 26:38.590
With me here,

26:39.960 --> 26:41.490
she won't be in any trouble.

26:43.160 --> 26:44.090
What do we do now?

26:44.630 --> 26:45.590
With half the military power,

26:45.590 --> 26:47.160
Mrs. Fan gets no benefit at all.

26:47.160 --> 26:48.890
She's likely just a scapegoat.

26:49.160 --> 26:51.070
The Grand Tutor
will surely be displeased too.

26:51.070 --> 26:52.550
Grandfather clearly wants to use Mrs. Fan

26:52.550 --> 26:54.000
to disrupt the Wei faction's plans.

26:54.000 --> 26:57.130
But it doesn't matter.
We can beat them at their own game.

26:57.590 --> 26:58.700
I, Li Huai'an,

26:59.160 --> 27:01.090
can also become Mrs. Fan's backer.

27:08.480 --> 27:09.680
My goodness.

27:10.830 --> 27:12.440
Chief Commandant?

27:13.270 --> 27:15.790
A reward of 100 taels of gold
and 500 taels of silver?

27:15.790 --> 27:16.750
Good heavens.

27:17.160 --> 27:20.590
It's enough for Changyu and Changning
to spend for a lifetime.

27:20.590 --> 27:21.790
That's nothing.

27:21.830 --> 27:22.590
Commandant Fan

27:22.590 --> 27:25.070
has half the military power in Jizhou.

27:25.720 --> 27:26.720
Young man,

27:27.030 --> 27:28.270
when you go back,

27:28.350 --> 27:30.480
tell our Changyu

27:30.480 --> 27:31.960
that although she's been promoted
to Commandant,

27:31.960 --> 27:33.590
there is a saying among the people:

27:33.590 --> 27:35.680
"A husband who shared your hardships
should not be cast aside."

27:35.680 --> 27:38.090
"A husband who shared your hardships"?
It's "wife."

27:38.090 --> 27:39.240
Don't interrupt.

27:40.270 --> 27:42.350
When Changyu was having such a hard time,

27:42.350 --> 27:44.000
it was Yan Zheng who was with her,

27:44.000 --> 27:45.440
supporting her through it all.

27:45.440 --> 27:47.480
Later, he was even conscripted
because of her.

27:47.480 --> 27:48.400
This bond

27:48.510 --> 27:50.150
is unlike any other.

27:50.240 --> 27:51.550
Tell her not to become like
those heartless women

27:51.550 --> 27:54.440
who turn their backs on their husbands
once they get rich.

27:54.440 --> 27:55.700
It's "heartless men."

27:55.750 --> 27:56.270
Dear,

27:56.270 --> 27:57.960
why do you keep

27:57.960 --> 27:58.880
interrupting me?

27:58.880 --> 27:59.960
Stop interrupting!

27:59.960 --> 28:00.880
But you said it wrong,

28:00.880 --> 28:02.940
and you won't let people correct you?

28:04.070 --> 28:05.200
Mr. Zhao, Mrs. Zhao,

28:05.550 --> 28:06.480
rest assured.

28:06.750 --> 28:09.000
Changyu is not that kind of person.

28:11.640 --> 28:13.310
I will definitely go back
and tell Commandant Fan

28:13.310 --> 28:15.030
and Mar...

28:16.880 --> 28:17.810
My good brother.

28:19.310 --> 28:21.350
Yan Zheng must return safely too.

28:21.630 --> 28:23.610
A family ought to be all together.

28:23.750 --> 28:26.240
Yes. Everyone in Lin'an
is waiting for him.

28:27.880 --> 28:28.790
I will surely

28:28.790 --> 28:30.320
deliver your words to them.

28:31.670 --> 28:34.220
[Knowledge is Boundless]

28:34.720 --> 28:35.550
Your Highness, I didn't expect you

28:35.550 --> 28:37.270
to travel all the way to the Northwest,
enduring such hardship,

28:37.270 --> 28:39.670
just for the Headmaster of Luyuan Academy.

28:42.640 --> 28:44.900
We reached an agreement for his sake too.

28:46.920 --> 28:47.950
Discipline Inspector Li,
you stay in Jizhou

28:47.950 --> 28:49.600
and refuse to return to the Capital.

28:49.600 --> 28:52.130
Surely you aren't pining
for a married woman?

28:53.590 --> 28:55.930
Mrs. Fan and the Marquis of Wu'an
are in a fake marriage.

28:55.930 --> 28:57.810
Commandant Fan and I are comrades.

28:57.810 --> 28:59.940
There's nothing improper between us.

29:00.920 --> 29:03.110
The Headmaster and I
once fought side by side.

29:03.110 --> 29:05.370
What we have is a righteous comradeship.

29:08.750 --> 29:10.410
Commandant Fan, you're here?

29:13.110 --> 29:14.200
If there was nothing improper,

29:14.200 --> 29:16.030
why are you so flustered?

29:16.550 --> 29:18.070
You really care about your comrade.

29:18.070 --> 29:20.270
Your Highness, please stop teasing me.

29:23.720 --> 29:24.550
Mr. Gongsun.

29:24.790 --> 29:27.320
You can't use the same trick
to tease someone.

29:28.550 --> 29:32.410
I didn't expect Your Highness
and Discipline Inspector Li to be here.

29:32.720 --> 29:34.190
Pardon my intrusion.

29:40.990 --> 29:41.760
Wenkan.

29:43.830 --> 29:45.370
The dressing has been changed.

29:45.370 --> 29:47.040
Get plenty of rest these days.

29:47.830 --> 29:49.030
I have things to do.

29:49.200 --> 29:50.260
I'll take my leave.

29:53.720 --> 29:55.840
Don't move. Count down from five.

29:56.030 --> 30:00.960
Five, four, three, two, one.

30:05.160 --> 30:06.290
Your Highness, I...

30:06.960 --> 30:09.020
Her Highness doesn't want to see you.

30:10.830 --> 30:11.690
Your Highness!

30:12.830 --> 30:14.430
Please wait, Your Highness!

30:14.720 --> 30:15.580
Your Highness.

30:16.030 --> 30:17.200
Let me explain, Your Highness.

30:17.200 --> 30:19.130
Stay away from the Princess Royal!

30:20.790 --> 30:21.650
Your Highness!

30:21.720 --> 30:23.270
Here's the thing, Your Highness!

30:23.270 --> 30:24.920
-Close the door.
-Let me explain.

30:24.920 --> 30:25.780
Your Highness!

30:26.310 --> 30:27.510
Are you leaving or not?

30:27.510 --> 30:28.590
No.

30:29.640 --> 30:31.700
If you don't go, I'll crush your foot.

30:39.590 --> 30:40.510
Are you alright?

30:40.510 --> 30:41.240
Let me see.

30:41.640 --> 30:42.830
I-I'm fine.

30:44.230 --> 30:44.880
I'm fine.

30:48.510 --> 30:49.770
You deceived me again?

30:52.200 --> 30:54.700
I just want to say a few words to you.

30:55.340 --> 30:56.690
Your Highness, tell me,

30:56.830 --> 30:57.830
do you have feelings for Li Huai'an...

30:57.830 --> 30:58.890
Feelings? My foot!

30:59.310 --> 31:00.960
Not only do I have no interest in him,

31:00.960 --> 31:02.550
I have no interest in you either.

31:02.550 --> 31:04.480
You came to find me just to say this?

31:05.790 --> 31:07.520
Do you have nothing else to say?

31:13.960 --> 31:16.000
Actually, I...

31:17.480 --> 31:18.680
Headmaster Gongsun.

31:19.880 --> 31:21.640
If you have no interest in me,

31:22.680 --> 31:24.740
then do not come looking for me again.

31:36.270 --> 31:39.190
[Knowledge is Boundless]

31:39.640 --> 31:41.110
Oh, this mouth.

31:41.110 --> 31:43.350
Why can't I say it at the crucial moment?

31:49.160 --> 31:50.090
Come on, Sister!

31:55.200 --> 31:55.960
Fan,

31:56.200 --> 31:58.000
why are you so distracted today?

31:58.070 --> 31:59.270
Should we keep going?

32:00.880 --> 32:01.480
Yes.

32:09.070 --> 32:10.280
Sorry, Lord Li.

32:12.830 --> 32:13.760
Commandant Fan,

32:14.000 --> 32:16.400
I came today
to discuss something with you.

32:20.920 --> 32:22.270
That matrilocal husband is annoying,

32:22.270 --> 32:23.400
and Li Menkan...

32:23.400 --> 32:24.660
is even more annoying.

32:27.200 --> 32:28.460
Lord Li, please leave.

32:28.790 --> 32:30.440
I am not in a good mood today.

32:32.070 --> 32:33.310
As you've just been appointed Commandant,

32:33.310 --> 32:35.830
you need to understand
the local military situation quickly.

32:35.830 --> 32:38.000
I hope this marked map can help you.

32:38.960 --> 32:40.310
If there is anything you don't understand,

32:40.310 --> 32:42.110
I am willing to explain it to you.

32:43.590 --> 32:46.920
Someone really likes to take advantage
of others' absence.

32:47.190 --> 32:50.440
I guess our matrilocal husband
is in trouble.

32:54.710 --> 32:55.680
In that case,

32:56.550 --> 32:57.790
thank you, Lord Li.

32:58.880 --> 33:01.100
You can leave if you don't want to listen.

33:01.100 --> 33:01.980
Not at all.

33:02.070 --> 33:03.530
We certainly can't leave.

33:03.640 --> 33:04.720
If we leave,

33:05.910 --> 33:07.840
who will protect your reputation?

34:14.320 --> 34:15.030
Great!

34:15.230 --> 34:15.960
Time to eat?

34:16.920 --> 34:18.179
It's such a great line!

34:22.150 --> 34:23.230
It's getting late.

34:23.480 --> 34:24.840
Let's call it a day.

34:24.880 --> 34:26.880
I've been tied up
with too many affairs recently.

34:26.880 --> 34:29.280
I'm afraid I can't accompany you
for the next few days.

34:29.280 --> 34:31.280
However, I've hired
the best teacher in Jizhou for you

34:31.280 --> 34:32.280
as your advisor.

34:32.469 --> 34:34.960
I believe you'll become
more like a commandant.

34:34.960 --> 34:36.440
Thank you, Lord Li.

34:37.150 --> 34:41.110
A Stratagem Against the Enemy:
Seize the Opportunity to Take the Sheep.

34:41.110 --> 34:43.400
"You must exploit every small gap

34:41.170 --> 34:43.679
[Knowledge is Boundless]

34:43.590 --> 34:46.070
and seize even the tiniest gains."

34:47.070 --> 34:48.110
I know this one.

34:48.440 --> 34:50.760
It means if I see a villain's sheep,

34:50.860 --> 34:52.070
I take it away in passing

34:52.070 --> 34:53.730
and make a mutton soup with it.

34:54.320 --> 34:55.920
That... that's kinda right.

34:56.420 --> 34:57.110
And this one.

34:57.110 --> 34:58.320
I know this one too.

34:58.510 --> 35:00.000
Kill with a Borrowed Knife.

35:00.000 --> 35:02.960
It means if I lose my blade
on the battlefield,

35:03.110 --> 35:04.760
I immediately borrow someone else's weapon

35:04.760 --> 35:06.620
and hack those bastards to death.

35:06.630 --> 35:08.830
You don't have to use your own strength.

35:09.110 --> 35:10.630
You induce others

35:10.630 --> 35:12.570
to eliminate the enemy for you.

35:12.630 --> 35:15.000
This allows you to save your own strength.

35:16.710 --> 35:17.630
Understood.

35:17.880 --> 35:20.960
Then I definitely know this
"Watch the Fire Burning Across the River."

35:20.960 --> 35:22.230
Back in our town,

35:22.230 --> 35:23.230
rich families

35:23.360 --> 35:25.710
get to watch the fireworks up close.

35:25.920 --> 35:27.530
But for us poor kids,

35:27.560 --> 35:29.580
we can only watch from very,

35:29.960 --> 35:31.300
very,

35:31.330 --> 35:33.070
very,

35:33.070 --> 35:34.130
very very far away.

35:35.440 --> 35:36.630
It's... It's... It's...

35:36.630 --> 35:39.030
It's not about fireworks.

35:41.230 --> 35:42.160
This... this...

35:42.590 --> 35:43.150
Next one.

35:45.740 --> 35:46.530
Sir,

35:46.590 --> 35:48.400
What does "Pointing at the Mulberry Tree and Scolding the Ghost" mean?

35:48.400 --> 35:52.130
It's "Pointing at the Mulberry Tree but Scolding the Locust Tree"!

35:56.960 --> 35:58.690
"For your kind correction..."

35:59.030 --> 36:00.760
-What does "For..."
-Changyu.

36:01.000 --> 36:01.670
Sir.

36:05.400 --> 36:06.860
How is the progress today?

36:08.960 --> 36:11.620
Commandant Fan is exceptionally intelligent.

36:12.110 --> 36:13.590
She learns by analogy.

36:14.400 --> 36:15.710
She is truly talented.

36:15.800 --> 36:17.190
You taught me well, Sir.

36:17.190 --> 36:18.190
You flatter me.

36:19.510 --> 36:21.190
Let's call it a day.

36:22.000 --> 36:22.920
Farewell.

36:22.920 --> 36:24.440
Sir, I've mastered Sun Tzu's Art of War.

36:24.440 --> 36:25.670
Tomorrow, can you teach me

36:25.670 --> 36:27.400
Sun Tzu's grandpa's art of war?

36:28.710 --> 36:29.550
Farewell.

36:30.630 --> 36:31.550
Sir!

36:37.150 --> 36:37.920
Hurry up

36:38.320 --> 36:39.780
and find another teacher.

36:40.760 --> 36:41.550
Got it.

36:42.110 --> 36:43.510
Thank you for your trouble, Mr. Liu.

36:43.510 --> 36:44.710
My students

36:44.890 --> 36:46.960
are the cream of the crop among generals.

36:46.960 --> 36:49.320
Discipline Inspector Li, you can rest assured.

36:49.320 --> 36:51.030
Don't worry.

36:52.320 --> 36:52.920
Please.

36:54.440 --> 36:55.030
Sir.

36:59.160 --> 36:59.970
[Qinwen Hall]

37:00.050 --> 37:03.690
[Knowledge is Boundless]

37:00.230 --> 37:01.440
Sir, you...

37:01.800 --> 37:03.440
She doesn't even know all the characters.

37:03.440 --> 37:05.510
You should find someone better qualified.

37:05.510 --> 37:06.510
Sir! Sir!

37:06.510 --> 37:07.960
I really can't help you.

37:07.960 --> 37:08.560
Farewell.

37:14.190 --> 37:14.840
My Lord.

37:14.970 --> 37:16.500
-This...
-Keep searching.

37:16.760 --> 37:18.400
Please rest assured, Discipline Inspector.

37:18.400 --> 37:19.710
I teach everyone without discrimination.

37:19.710 --> 37:24.520
[Knowledge is Boundless]

37:20.320 --> 37:20.960
Sir.

37:21.480 --> 37:21.880
Sir.

37:21.880 --> 37:22.920
Even if I have to die of poverty,

37:22.920 --> 37:23.800
I won't teach her anymore!

37:23.800 --> 37:24.760
Sir! S-

37:24.840 --> 37:26.960
There's no one who can't be taught.

37:27.480 --> 37:28.880
I am not learned enough.

37:28.960 --> 37:30.190
Please, Discipline Inspector Li,
have mercy

37:30.190 --> 37:31.070
and spare my life!

37:31.070 --> 37:32.130
-Sir, get up!
-Sir!

37:51.660 --> 37:55.010
[Recruitment for a Good Teacher]

37:59.320 --> 38:00.440
The student

38:00.440 --> 38:02.100
isn't Commandant Fan, is she?

38:02.110 --> 38:02.760
It is.

38:04.190 --> 38:04.840
Sir!

38:08.330 --> 38:14.560
[Jizhou Government Office]

38:08.400 --> 38:09.070
My Lord.

38:09.510 --> 38:10.400
Commandant Fan's reputation

38:10.400 --> 38:12.200
has spread throughout the city.

38:12.320 --> 38:14.520
I've raised the offer to 3 taels an hour.

38:14.610 --> 38:19.490
[Recruitment for a Good Teacher]

38:14.800 --> 38:15.480
Forget it.

38:16.250 --> 38:17.510
I'll teach her myself.

38:19.690 --> 38:25.840
[Three days later]

38:25.150 --> 38:26.760
How did this happen?

38:29.150 --> 38:30.440
Commandant Fan did it.

38:31.030 --> 38:32.400
You're both still injured,

38:32.400 --> 38:34.400
and you actually started sparring?

38:37.110 --> 38:38.710
It's all internal injuries.

38:40.400 --> 38:41.760
It's getting late.

38:43.030 --> 38:44.110
Help me up.

38:44.440 --> 38:45.970
I still have to go teach her.

38:46.710 --> 38:48.030
You should rest.

38:48.480 --> 38:49.920
Let's stop teaching Commandant Fan.

38:49.920 --> 38:51.110
Learning the art of war

38:51.110 --> 38:52.630
needs to be done step by step,

38:52.630 --> 38:53.150
Right?

38:53.150 --> 38:54.660
Learning the art of war?

38:55.710 --> 38:56.550
It's the first time I've seen

38:56.550 --> 38:58.670
someone get hurt just from teaching.

39:00.800 --> 39:01.920
Lord Li?

39:04.150 --> 39:04.840
Changyu.

39:05.590 --> 39:07.840
Lord Li, please don't!

39:07.960 --> 39:08.710
Lord Li.

39:10.440 --> 39:12.150
Lord Li, I am truly sorry.

39:13.510 --> 39:16.360
Maybe I should just learn slowly
by myself.

39:17.230 --> 39:18.070
Well,

39:18.230 --> 39:20.030
my godfather is so formidable.

39:20.400 --> 39:22.800
He even wanted to take me
as a disciple at first.

39:22.800 --> 39:24.360
Is it because he's getting old

39:24.360 --> 39:25.960
and his eyes are failing him?

39:26.150 --> 39:27.760
Mrs. Fan,

39:28.000 --> 39:29.860
you surely possess great wisdom.

39:30.000 --> 39:32.670
Grand Tutor Tao must have seen that in you.

39:32.960 --> 39:34.320
I cannot compare to him.

39:36.250 --> 39:37.080
I think so too.

39:39.390 --> 39:40.320
Well,

39:40.510 --> 39:42.570
should I ask my godfather to teach me?

39:42.790 --> 39:44.950
Let's not torture the old man.

40:13.960 --> 40:16.150
Why can't I learn it?

40:17.670 --> 40:20.130
It seems I'm really not cut out for studying.

40:37.150 --> 40:38.880
In the margins of the paragraphs,

40:38.880 --> 40:40.360
I wrote notes in red.

40:41.360 --> 40:43.360
Read them slowly when you have time.

40:58.070 --> 40:59.440
"Though storm and darkness fill the sky

40:59.440 --> 41:01.150
and the rooster crows without end,

41:01.150 --> 41:02.410
now that I have met you—

41:02.440 --> 41:04.240
how could my heart not rejoice?"

41:04.550 --> 41:05.710
The meaning of this poem line

41:05.710 --> 41:06.630
is that

41:06.840 --> 41:08.570
amidst the dark, pouring rain,

41:08.710 --> 41:10.240
the roosters crow in panic.

41:11.100 --> 41:13.500
Yet, precisely in this chaotic moment,

41:14.320 --> 41:15.360
I glance around,

41:16.590 --> 41:17.960
and I catch sight of her.

41:18.840 --> 41:19.710
It's like

41:20.070 --> 41:21.670
pushing through the clouds,

41:21.840 --> 41:23.700
and a beam of light falls upon you.

41:25.070 --> 41:26.190
warm and radiant,

41:27.320 --> 41:28.780
filling my heart with joy.

41:31.400 --> 41:32.840
Why is it that when Yan Zheng taught me,

41:32.840 --> 41:33.970
I could remember it?

41:42.280 --> 41:43.960
I wonder what he's doing.
